headline: Smurfit Westrock (SW) Records Q2 Net Loss Tied to Restructuring Costs
summary: Smurfit Westrock Plc (NYSE:SW) is placed 10th on our list of the best stocks to buy. The company recorded a net loss of $26 million in Q2 2025, compared to $132 million in the same quarter last year, as restructuring costs tempered its results. headline: IP, Novolex, Smurfit Westrock among companies with August layoff announcements
summary: At least seven companies announced temporary and permanent layoffs that are slated to affect employees in multiple states, most prominently in Georgia and California.
